      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　mihoさん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! miho-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.9333340327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "くっ！　川咲さくら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh! Sakura Kawasaki…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9333340327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "お休みの日に偶然出会うってなんだか嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad we met by chance on my day off",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.966667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.966667366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "私は嬉しくないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not glad about it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.766667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6333340327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言わずに、偶然の出会いを楽しみましょう！\nmihoさんもお休みですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't say that‚ let's enjoy our chance meeting!\nAre you also off today‚ miho-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6333340327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……そうね。これからジムに行ってトレーニングよ\nだから、貴方にかまっている暇はないの。それじゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… yes. I'm going to the gym for a training\nSo‚ I have no reason to get involved with you. Then‚ goodbye",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1333346684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.1333346684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "待って下さい！　ジムなんてさすが大人ですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute! Going to the gym? You're an an adult~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0333346684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.0333346684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "体を鍛えてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you working out your body?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.0666680018
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それ以外ジムで何をするの？　あとは持久力もつけるわ\nだから私は忙しいの。それじゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What else do you do at the gym? I also build stamina\nThat's why I'm busy. Then‚ farewell",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0666680018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お、お待ちを！　ジムってその……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait! The gym…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5666680018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.5666680018
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "会員さんじゃないとダメなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't I enter if I'm not a member?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ワンデイパスとか無料体験とかあるんじゃないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are there any one-day passes or free trials?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5000013351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5000013351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "自分で調べて。本当にもう行くわ。それじゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look it up yourself. I'm really going now. Bye",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "な、泣きの一回！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "J-Just one more thing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2333346684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.2333346684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いい加減にして！　私はジムに行きたいの。分かる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Enough! I want to go to the gym. Do you understand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7666700363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.7666700363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "邪魔しないでもらえる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can you please stop bothering me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えーっと、その～実は私もジムに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heyー‚ um~‚ actually‚ I was thinking about",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8666700363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8666700363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "行ってみたいなーなんて思いまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "going to the gymー too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ……もう勝手にして。このまま拘束されるより",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… Just do whatever you want. It's better than",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6666700363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.6666700363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "マシだわ。でも、あっちで話しかけないでちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "being stuck with you. But don't bother me later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わーい！　mihoさんとオフに遊べるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yayー! I'm so happy I got hang out with miho-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.133336703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.133336703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいなぁ！　みんなにグループメッセで報告して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "on our day off! I'll have to send a group message to everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "やめなさい！　あくまでジムを紹介するだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't do it! I'm just introducing you about the gym",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2333346684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2333346684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "貴方と大切な休日を過ごす訳じゃないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not spending my precious day off with you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それでもいいんです！　私はmihoさんと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's okay! I'm really happy that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8333346684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.8333346684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "仲良くなれた気がしてすっごく嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've become close with miho-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
